<DOC><DOCNO> DOE1-54-1274 </DOCNO><TEXT>An improved directional coupler has been designed, fabricated and testedin order to measure the high-level power of microwave produced by a gyrotron.It has shown a sufficient function requisite in electron cyclotron resonanceheating experiments of magnetically confined plasmas. The results oftests under practical experimental conditions are described and variouspoints to be taken in the design of a directional coupler are given.</TEXT></DOC>